message: MEMBRANE DIRECT INTEGRITY (DIT) TEST -  Complete DIT, If The Maximum Allowed Time Without A DIT Has Been Exceeded

GENERAL SYSTEM - FILL Membrane Feed & Filtrate Sides With Water
